9. Develop and demonstrate, using JavaScript script, a XHTML document 
that contains three short paragraphs of text, stacked on top of each other, 
with only enough of each showing so that the mouse cursor can be placed over some part of them. 
When the cursor is placed over the exposed part of any paragraph, it should rise to the
top to become completely visible



<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>Stacking Paragraphs</title>

    <style>
        .box {
            width: 250px;
            padding: 15px;
            border: 2px solid black;
            position: absolute;
        }

        #box1 {
            background: yellow;
            top: 100px;
            left: 100px;
            z-index: 1;
        }

        #box2 {
            background: lightblue;
            top: 120px;
            left: 120px;
            z-index: 2;
        }

        #box3 {
            background: lightgreen;
            top: 140px;
            left: 140px;
            z-index: 3;
        }
    </style>

    <script>
        function mover(id)
        {
            document.getElementById("box1").style.zIndex = 1;
            document.getElementById("box2").style.zIndex = 2;
            document.getElementById("box3").style.zIndex = 3;

            document.getElementById(id).style.zIndex = 10
        }
    </script>

</head>

<body>

<h2>Stacking of Paragraphs</h2>

<div id="box1" class="box" onmouseover="mover('box1')">
 
    Honesty is the best policy. Honest people are trusted by everyone.
    They always speak the truth and do the right thing, even when it is difficult.
</div>

<div id="box2" class="box" onmouseover="mover('box2')">
    
    A thirsty crow found a pot with very little water.
    It dropped small stones into the pot until the water level rose,
    then it drank the water. This teaches us that intelligence solves problems.
</div>

<div id="box3" class="box" onmouseover="mover('box3')">
   
    Slow and steady wins the race. A tortoise challenged a hare to a race.
    The hare slept on the way, while the tortoise kept moving and won the race.
</div>

</body>
</html>
